OL,3,CBurnham will be next prime minister
OL,4,Cafter 349 MPs back him as Labour leader
OL,6,FAndy Burnham will be the next prime
OL,7,Fminister after he received an extra 27
OL,8,Fnominations from Labour MPs on Monday,
OL,9,Ftaking his total to 349.
OL,11,FThe additional nominations, on top of
OL,12,Fthe 322 he received last week, mean it
OL,13,Fis now impossible for any other
OL,14,Fcandidate to gain the 81 endorsements
OL,15,Fneeded to challenge for the Labour
OL,16,Fleadership.
OL,18,FWhile almost 80% of the Parliamentary
OL,19,FLabour Party formally nominated
OL,20,FBurnham last week, extra endorsements
OL,21,Fon Monday took him over the line.
