OL,3,CBurnham will be next prime minister
OL,4,Cafter 349 MPs back him as Labour leader
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FAs the only candidate to replace Sir
OL,12,FKeir Starmer, Burnham is expected to
OL,13,Fformally take over the Labour
OL,14,Fleadership at a special party
OL,15,Fconference on Friday.
OL,17,FHe will then become prime minister
OL,18,Fthree days later, on July 20.
